# Hakuto environment variables
#
# 1. Copy this file:    cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Fill in your keys  (the .env.local file is gitignored — safe for secrets)
# 3. Restart Claude Code so the new values are loaded

# PageSpeed Insights API key — required by the /pagespeed-audit skill.
# Get a free key in ~1 minute (no billing required):
